column5: The smallies out this way are starting to move to the fall hangouts,been getting 30 to 40,with some hogs thrown in each time out.
Some Serious Smallies right there  :worthy:  .......I'll be heading there this weekend
Beautiful fish Larry. You gotta love the colours on those critters. You make me sick.
a couple very nice bronze backs for sure !!!! cheers
Awesome bass Larry.  Also nice to hear someone say 'early' fall.
Nice ones !!!!! Thers nothing like fall smallies
Great photos! Nothing better than a fall smallie bite - Their fat, aggressive and plentiful!
